  1Ôćĺ// Mock OAuth server for E2E testing.
  2Ôćĺ// Implements /authorize (PKCE + state), /token (code exchange + refresh), and /calls (request log).
  3Ôćĺ// Usage: node mock-oauth-server.js
  4Ôćĺ// Prints JSON to stdout: { "port": <number> }
